    <h1 class="font-bold text-2xl">Setup your survey rationale</h1>
    <p class="mx-14 mt-4 text-center">Welcome to the "Rationale" screen, where you have the power to bring your survey to life! By adding your rationale, you unlock a deeper understanding of your respondents' thoughts and motivations. This is your chance to shine a light on the reasons behind the data, uncovering the fascinating story within. Don't let your survey remain a mystery - illuminate it with the power of rationale! Get ready to unravel insights like never before and make your survey truly impactful.</p>

    <div class="w-full mt-6 mx-12">
        <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="normal">Title</label>
            <input id="normal" class="form-input w-full" type="text" placeholder="" />
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="normal">Description</label>
            <textarea id="normal" class="form-input w-full" type="text" placeholder=""></textarea>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-4">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="normal">Photos</label>

            <header
        class="mt-4 border-dashed border-2 border-gray-400 py-12 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
        <p class="mb-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 flex flex-wrap justify-center">
            <span>Drag and drop your</span>&nbsp;<span>files anywhere or</span>
        </p>
        <input id="hidden-input" type="file" multiple class="hidden" />
        <button id="button"
            class="mt-2 rounded-sm px-3 py-1 bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 focus:shadow-outline focus:outline-none">
            Upload a file
        </button>
        <br>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Maximum size of 3MB</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Accepted files are only: .xlsx, .xls, .csv</span>
    </header>
